WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:04.000
No, thank you. The two of you have shown how important love is.

00:04.720 --> 00:09.440
Now I would like to give both of you a gift, your very own Pegasus.

00:09.440 --> 00:14.000
You can ride her anywhere in the Cloud Kingdom, wherever your heart desires.

00:14.000 --> 00:17.280
Now go, head to the Pegasus' quarters to pick one out.

